## Testing Requirements

Every tool function must pass these test cases:
- [ ] Non-existent ticker → returns error, not fabricated data
- [ ] KODEX brand + non-Samsung ticker → caught by validator  
- [ ] API timeout → returns null fields, not estimates
- [ ] Same ETF queried twice → identical static data both times
- [ ] Known ticker-name pairs match master DB exactly
- [ ] Fee values match master DB (not LLM memory)
